ClawKeeper includes derivative work based in part on NVIDIA NemoClaw and is designed to operate with NVIDIA OpenShell and OpenClaw.

This repository preserves upstream license and attribution notices in source files where applicable and adds ClawKeeper-specific modifications, documentation, and roadmap material.

ClawKeeper is an independent derivative project. References to NVIDIA, NemoClaw, OpenShell, OpenClaw, or other third-party names are used to describe project origin, interoperability, or compatibility. All third-party marks remain the property of their respective owners.
